faith in that statement.

00:04:42.657 --> 00:04:43.491 position:50% align:center
[ALL]
Hm?

00:04:43.533 --> 00:04:46.161 position:50% align:center
Oh, Kuragi.

00:04:48.621 --> 00:04:49.456 position:50% align:center
Machi.

00:04:49.497 --> 00:04:50.123 position:50% align:center
