00:04:50.165 --> 00:04:53.043 position:50% align:center
You see? That means
it must be true.

00:04:53.084 --> 00:04:56.671 position:50% align:center
[KIMI]
Oh, Machi. No, how could you?

00:04:56.713 --> 00:04:59.049 position:50% align:center
Hey, uh, what happened
to having faith?

00:04:59.090 --> 00:05:03.303 position:50% align:center
I think where Kimi's concerned,
faith is a fickle thing.

00:05:05.055 --> 00:05:06.806 position:50% align:center
[MACHI'S MOTHER]
I don't want to hear it!

00:05:06.848 --> 00:05:09.851 position:50% align:center
