from the day he was born.

00:05:09.893 --> 00:05:11.311 position:50% align:center
[MACHI'S FATHER] I've worried
that might be the case

00:05:11.353 --> 00:05:12.562 position:50% align:center
for a while.

00:05:12.604 --> 00:05:14.939 position:50% align:center
I don't think you should
live here anymore.

00:05:14.981 --> 00:05:17.192 position:50% align:center
It'll be better
for you this way.

00:05:17.233 --> 00:05:19.903 position:50% align:center
Yes. This is for your sake.

00:05:19.944 --> 00:05:23.990 position:50% align:center
[MACHI'S MOTHER] You'll feel
more comfortable on your own.

00:05:24.032 --> 00:05:26.951 position:50% align:center
[MANABE]
So, about this rumor.

00:05:26.993 --> 00:05:27.827 position:50% align:center
I hate to say it,

00:05:27.869 --> 00:05:31.623 position:50% align:center
but it's actually pretty
close to the truth.

00:05:31.664 --> 00:05:33.416 position:50% align:center
Machi has a little brother.

00:05:33.458 --> 00:05:35.627 position:50% align:center
I mean, he's my
half-brother, too.

00:05:35.669 --> 00:05:39.673 position:50% align:center
And he's young.
Way younger than us.

00:05:39.714 --> 00:05:42.050 position:50% align:center
Machi and I were both
deemed unsuitable,

00:05:42.092 --> 00:05:44.969 position:50% align:center
so they decided to name him
the heir of the family.

00:05:45.011 --> 00:05:48.139 position:50% align:center
And I guess that decision
didn't sit too well with her.

00:05:48.181 --> 00:05:50.392 position:50% align:center
She got jealous and
tried to kill him.

00:05:50.433 --> 00:05:51.976 position:50% align:center
They couldn't have her
around after that,

00:05:52.018 --> 00:05:54.229 position:50% align:center
