with her own place.

00:05:54.270 --> 00:05:57.941 position:50% align:center
Yeah, I don't know. That sounds
pretty hard to believe.

00:05:57.982 --> 00:05:59.150 position:50% align:center
Fair point.

00:05:59.192 --> 00:06:01.277 position:50% align:center
That's what I heard
from the parentals,

00:06:01.319 --> 00:06:03.822 position:50% align:center
so who knows how warped it is?

00:06:03.863 --> 00:06:05.657 position:50% align:center
We could always go ask Machi.

00:06:05.699 --> 00:06:06.866 position:50% align:center
[YUKI gasps]

00:06:06.908 --> 00:06:09.411 position:50% align:center
Go and see her.
Find out the truth.

00:06:09.452 --> 00:06:13.707 position:50% align:center
What? No! We can't
do that. She lives alone.

00:06:13.748 --> 00:06:15.500 position:50% align:center
