00:06:15.542 --> 00:06:18.169 position:50% align:center
Nothin' about her place
is remotely sexy.

00:06:18.211 --> 00:06:20.171 position:50% align:center
[YUKI] Why is it always
about that with you?

00:06:20.213 --> 00:06:21.548 position:50% align:center
Oh, hey, you know,

00:06:21.589 --> 00:06:24.926 position:50% align:center
I remember this one winter
when it snowed like crazy.

00:06:24.968 --> 00:06:27.846 position:50% align:center
Please stop. This conversation
is giving me whiplash.

00:06:27.887 --> 00:06:30.432 position:50% align:center
Sorry, man, it just
now came to me.

00:06:30.473 --> 00:06:32.559 position:50% align:center
So there was a buncha snow

00:06:32.600 --> 00:06:35.145 position:50% align:center
and the whole family was
together for some reason.

00:06:35.186 --> 00:06:39.607 position:50% align:center
They were all being lame,
so I snuck out for a while.

00:06:39.649 --> 00:06:40.942 position:50% align:center
Huh?

00:06:40.984 --> 00:06:44.320 position:50% align:center
[MANABE] Turns out Machi
had the same idea.

00:06:44.362 --> 00:06:46.281 position:50% align:center
I watched her for a little bit.

00:06:46.322 --> 00:06:50.035 position:50% align:center
She was walking around,
leaving footprints in the snow.

00:06:50.076 --> 00:06:53.288 position:50% align:center
She was super intent on it.
Just round and round.

00:06:53.329 --> 00:06:54.956 position:50% align:center
Dead silent.

00:06:54.998 --> 00:06:59.085 position:50% align:center
What could that have
been about, you think?

00:06:59.127 --> 00:07:01.796 position:50% align:center
[doorbell rings]

00:07:03.757 --> 00:07:05.884 position:50% align:center
Hey!

00:07:05.925 --> 00:07:07.010 position:50% align:center
[MACHI yelps]

00:07:07.052 --> 00:07:08.595 position:50% align:center
Thanks for havin' us!

00:07:08.636 --> 00:07:11.431 position:50% align:center
Come right in, Yun-Yun!
Don't be shy!

00:07:11.473 --> 00:07:13.641 position:50% align:center
[YUKI]
Hey, would you let me go?

00:07:14.934 --> 00:07:17.145 position:50% align:center
Sure enough, it's as
messy as always.

00:07:17.187 --> 00:07:18.521 position:50% align:center
Go away!

00:07:18.563 --> 00:07:20.982 position:50% align:center
Oh, wow, this brings
back memories.

00:07:21.024 --> 00:07:22.192 position:50% align:center
It's the Toxic Jungle!

00:07:22.233 --> 00:07:23.651 position:50% align:center
[MACHI]
Get out!

00:07:23.693 --> 00:07:25.987 position:50% align:center
Yun-Yun. Here, for you.

00:07:26.029 --> 00:07:27.238 position:50% align:center
Yeah?

00:07:27.280 --> 00:07:28.573 position:50% align:center
What's...?

00:07:31.368 --> 00:07:32.911 position:50% align:center
